  <brief_title>Erector Spinae Plane Block for Postoperative Analgesia for Laparoscopic Cholecystectomy</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effect of Erector Spinae Plane Block on Postoperative Pain Following Laparoscopic Cholecystectomy: A Randomized Controlled Study</official_title>
